oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: The Quiz Kids - #429 - Excerpt part 1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Part 1 of an excerpt of NBC radio program The Quiz Kids episode #429, originally broadcast 1948-09-05. Hosted by Joe Kelly with announcer Bob Murphy, and special guest Gene Autry.
